{"tid":124354,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"終於睇左比利林恩的中場戰事,根本就係講緊點解要反對人大831","createTime":"2017-02-17T13:54:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-18T09:41:12.000Z","uid":49391,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2d5a25d347bddd21197c0f681fdf9e0a0bc7cbcd","tid":124354,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T13:54:24.000Z","msg":"從前有班美軍返到美國,遇到一個老闆有興趣將佢地GE英雄故事拍成電影<br />\n(從前,有個地方叫香港回歸中國,並承諾會有普選)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/834mv87.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F834mv87.jpg&h=1a5b748e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但果個老闆只係肯出每人五千五百美金<br />\n(但中共只係肯推個831假普選方案出黎)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SsB224m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSsB224m.jpg&h=f181e7d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就好似施捨乞衣一樣<br />\n(就好似當我地香港人係乞兒一樣)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xjrR458.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxjrR458.jpg&h=0311314a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n班美軍覺得每人十萬先係合理<br />\n(香港人覺得要有公民提名先係合理)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b0mTGod.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb0mTGod.jpg&h=eaf32dde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然呢個要求係樂觀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9UZES0S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9UZES0S.jpg&h=92738532&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係佢(我)地應得嘅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sg48XWJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSg48XWJ.jpg&h=fc7f159c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n老闆只係肯出每人五千五百美金<br />\n(中共只係肯推出831方案)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XQSUxf6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXQSUxf6.jpg&h=5eb911a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n並且毫不讓步<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZfOe599.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZfOe599.jpg&h=fb2ac505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n老闆覺得五千五百聊勝於無,你地唔要就罷<br />\n(有D香港人覺得831都算係一種民主進步,袋住先,有好過無)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P5VZm95.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP5VZm95.jpg&h=4a12ff65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n太可悲了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/95crx1E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F95crx1E.jpg&h=0e43d9ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(中共咁辛苦爭取返香港回歸,以為中共會鍾意我地,點知一過蜜月期就原型畢露)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wwr0x9u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWwr0x9u.jpg&h=b358d73f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSometimes nothing is better than something.<br />\n(與其整埋呢D 831袋住先,我地情願唔要)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C8FW87w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC8FW87w.jpg&h=2c267559&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(可能對一D港豬/藍屍黎講)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T5Y398d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT5Y398d.jpg&h=34bb869b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(袋住先,總好過乜都無吖)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z2K6Qmt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz2K6Qmt.jpg&h=580d032c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(唔得,我地必須追求我地認為啱嘅事)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p7uA2i6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp7uA2i6.jpg&h=b190e321&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(中共推呢套831出黎根本就假普選,愚蠢港人,扭曲左民主,我地要對假普選說不)<br />\n<br />\n同意請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c87ed27f305321f8be4cfc421118db13360d105","tid":124354,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T13:56:22.000Z","msg":"貼下GIF<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G6G0d45.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG6G0d45.gif&h=b5e927fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/91Z546m.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F91Z546m.gif&h=1bafc18d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UgfZZb5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUgfZZb5.gif&h=a0b4e294&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n畫面有D淒美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0e5c1f0204b821c503995624b87db7bb6b0182c","tid":124354,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T13:59:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/KX-JeV37Uqw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKX-JeV37Uqw&d=26VZ%2FvgZZ8DFpCmOvUDyu%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=3baf78da\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/KX-JeV37Uqw</a><br />\n<br />\n同埋睇完套戲想起一首歌:Billy Dont Be A Hero<br />\n如果用黎做主題歌應該好夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"467f7b39e6ca8a7f515a5893d101517134e185b7","tid":124354,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T14:11:26.000Z","msg":"其實同類型嘅戲黎講,我鍾意奇連伊士活果套戰火旗蹟多D<br />\n一樣係講戰爭英雄回國做馬騮戲,被媒眾大眾,去推銷戰爭債券,申明左形式主義對戰爭的必要性<br />\n畢竟對於戰爭呢D國家大事黎講,個人的榮辱係好小事<br />\n<br />\n但我唔係話比利林恩呢套戲講GE野係錯,只係對戰爭的一種唔同角度的睇法而已"},{"pid":"85ddbf20cc29eb12d46a8299f88c7c3d9f9519e1","tid":124354,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T14:11:45.000Z","msg":"其實同類型嘅戲黎講,我鍾意奇連伊士活果套戰火旗蹟多D<br />\n一樣係講戰爭英雄回國做馬騮戲,被媒眾大眾,去推銷戰爭債券,申明左形式主義對戰爭的必要性<br />\n畢竟對於戰爭呢D國家大事黎講,個人的榮辱係好小事<br />\n<br />\n但我唔係話比利林恩呢套戲講GE野係錯,只係對戰爭的一種唔同角度的睇法而已"},{"pid":"91612e10dfb6b00ebd72f92f120e088e389870f9","tid":124354,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T09:17:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實同類型嘅戲黎講,我鍾意奇連伊士活果套戰火旗蹟多D<br />\n一